title: Complain about a financial service or product

heading_context: Complain about a financial service or product
chunks.html_content:
Follow the company’s complaints procedure. You can usually then take your complaint to the Financial Ombudsman Service if you’re unhappy with their response.

Ask for a copy of the company’s complaints procedure. This should tell you how to complain and how they’ll deal with it.

If you’re unhappy with their response (or they do not respond within 8 weeks) you can complain to an independent complaints service. This is usually the Financial Ombudsman Service - the company’s complaints procedure should tell you which service to contact.
